223
00:12:28,688 --> 00:12:30,148
but you wronged me.

224
00:12:33,129 --> 00:12:34,189
All right.

225
00:12:35,529 --> 00:12:36,829
So, are you leaving?

226
00:12:38,289 --> 00:12:39,309
I'm not leaving.

227
00:12:41,529 --> 00:12:42,669
So, how's the pain?

228
00:12:43,088 --> 00:12:43,988
