244
00:14:46,129 --> 00:14:47,348
Xiao Ran,

245
00:14:48,249 --> 00:14:49,789
I was trying

246
00:14:50,088 --> 00:14:52,807
to talk Mr. Lin out of resigning.

247
00:14:52,808 --> 00:14:55,567
I didn't expect Xingtian to come out.

248
00:14:55,568 --> 00:14:57,348
I didn't want that to happen.

249
00:14:57,448 --> 00:14:59,748
I know why you went to see Qiao.

250
00:15:00,009 --> 00:15:01,268
Don't worry.

251
00:15:01,289 --> 00:15:02,469
I'm not mad.

252
00:15:03,009 --> 00:15:05,429
But Mr. Lin...

253
00:15:08,088 --> 00:15:11,069
Qiao wants to resign.

254
00:15:11,489 --> 00:15:13,087
I tried to talk him out of it
many times,

255
00:15:13,088 --> 00:15:14,709
but I couldn't persuade him.

256
00:15:15,609 --> 00:15:16,868
Just like you,

257
00:15:17,688 --> 00:15:19,429
