258
00:15:20,409 --> 00:15:22,108
But there's not much I can do.

259
00:15:31,968 --> 00:15:33,228
I'm sorry.

260
00:15:34,928 --> 00:15:37,567
I didn't want Mr. Lin

261
00:15:37,568 --> 00:15:40,429
